node.text: I had the pleasure of talking to Maisy about voting, the environment and her pop Joe the other day! If you haven’t voted already, visit iwillvote.com to make a plan to do so!!!! Making your voice heard, even if you are like me and not of voting age, is important today and everyday. ❤️❤️❤️❤️
